    <h3>ğŸ—ï¸ MVC Demo - Single Post View</h3>
    <p>This page demonstrates:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Data Relationships:</strong> Post â†’ Author, Post â†’ Comments</li>
        <li><strong>Dynamic Content:</strong> Post content, comment threading</li>
        <li><strong>Form Processing:</strong> Comment submission and validation</li>
        <li><strong>URL Parameters:</strong> Post ID routing (/posts/:id)</li>
    </ul>
    <p><small>ğŸ’¡ All data is stored in memory for this training demo</small></p>
</div>